data.description: Looking for space? You do not want to miss this beautiful and updated 4 bedroom with 2 and 1/2 bath home. Walking in you'll notice gleaming hardwood flooring in the living room (with gas fireplace) and dining room leading you to the large open kitchen with granite countertops, s/s appliances, island with barstool seating, custom closet pantry and upgraded lighting. First floor laundry conveniently off the garage. Upstairs has 2 full baths and 4 large bedrooms all with hardwood flooring. Master bathroom has double sinks, soaking tub and separate shower. Outside has a large fenced in yard and deck. New furnace in 2022. Some windows have been replaced. This location offers easy access to expressways and city amenities, ensuring a lifestyle of utmost convenience! Call to schedule your appointment today!
